summary: Tested 3 new integrated modules: codici_tributo_f24.py (F24 tax codes database), libro_unico_parser.py (Zucchetti payslip PDF parser), buste_paga.py router (payslip API), and comparatore.py router (price comparator API). Backend: 34/34 tests passed (100%).

minor.issue: safe_float() doesn't handle Italian number format with dots as thousands separator (e.g., '1.234,56')

critical_code_review_comments: codici_tributo_f24.py: Well-structured with 44 F24 tax codes covering ERARIO, INPS, REGIONI, IMU, INAIL sections. Functions for search, filtering by section, and code lookup work correctly.
libro_unico_parser.py: Comprehensive PDF parser for Zucchetti payslips with support for both dipendente and amministratore formats. Handles competenza month extraction with confidence levels.
buste_paga.py router: Complete CRUD API for payslip management with upload, save, list, riepilogo-mensile, and delete endpoints. Proper error handling for non-PDF files.
comparatore.py router: Full price comparator with product search, supplier management, cart functionality, product mapping, and supplier exclusion features.
seed_data_creation: Test data created for cart operations and product mapping (TEST_ prefixed, cleaned up after tests)
context_for_next_testing_agent: New modules integrated and tested: 1) codici_tributo_f24.py - F24 tax codes database with 44 codes, functions: get_codice_info, cerca_codice_tributo, get_all_codici, get_codici_by_sezione. 2) libro_unico_parser.py - Zucchetti payslip PDF parser with parse_libro_unico_pdf function. 3) buste_paga.py router - APIs: POST /api/buste-paga/upload, GET /api/buste-paga/competenze, GET /api/buste-paga/riepilogo-mensile/{competenza}, GET /api/buste-paga/lista. 4) comparatore.py router - APIs: GET /api/comparatore/products?search=, GET /api/comparatore/suppliers, GET /api/comparatore/cart, POST /api/comparatore/cart/add, DELETE /api/comparatore/cart/{id}.

libro_unico_parser.note: PDF parsing requires actual PDF file - utility functions tested
